00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:00:21,960 --> 00:00:23,128
Hi, Mom.

2
00:00:32,637 --> 00:00:33,847
[Sunok exhales]

3
00:00:35,849 --> 00:00:37,267
Well, if you're calling me that...

4
00:00:39,144 --> 00:00:41,647
...then I guess I really must be dying.

5
00:00:43,148 --> 00:00:46,151
GANGWON SAEBAEK HOSPITAL

6
