23
00:01:44,292 --> 00:01:46,128
I really hated my life here.

24
00:01:47,754 --> 00:01:49,548
And I resented you a lot, too.

25
00:01:51,550 --> 00:01:52,551
[Heeju inhales]

26
00:01:53,093 --> 00:01:56,513
[Heeju] It hurt every time you called me
a luckless brat

27
00:01:56,596 --> 00:01:59,015
or told me nothing will ever work out.

28
00:02:00,308 --> 00:02:01,977
Just give up and live with it.

29
00:02:03,979 --> 00:02:05,814
Just hearing you say those things...

30
00:02:08,066 --> 00:02:10,402
...made it impossible to even dream.

31
00:02:12,362 --> 00:02:13,613
But I realized...

32
00:02:14,448 --> 00:02:16,533
...that's just how you had
to live your life.

33
00:02:19,077 --> 00:02:21,913
[Heeju] And that's why I ran because
I didn't want to live like you.

34
