I thought that maybe...

35
00:02:26,668 --> 00:02:28,420
...if I just ran far enough...

36
00:02:29,963 --> 00:02:32,841
...I could find a way out of that long,
dark tunnel.

37
00:02:34,426 --> 00:02:36,052
[Heeju inhales]

38
00:02:37,095 --> 00:02:38,930
But no matter how far I ran...

39
00:02:39,014 --> 00:02:41,349
[Heeju inhales and exhales deeply]

40
00:02:42,225 --> 00:02:43,435
...there was no end.

41
00:02:45,562 --> 00:02:48,315
That's when I realized I wasn't in
a tunnel at all.

42
00:02:52,068 --> 00:02:53,695
I was in a mine shaft.

43
00:02:55,947 --> 00:02:57,657
