Was he your first love?

77
00:04:50,729 --> 00:04:51,771
[Sunok laughs]

78
00:04:53,940 --> 00:04:55,275
I guess.

79
00:04:57,485 --> 00:04:59,446
He was so handsome.
STYLE
::cue()

80
00:05:02,490 --> 00:05:04,326
One day when I was younger...

81
