00:18:45,479 --> 00:18:46,897
[Heeju] Close the trunk right now.

266
00:18:48,190 --> 00:18:49,442
The trunk! Close it!

267
00:18:51,318 --> 00:18:54,321
[exhales]

268
00:18:59,827 --> 00:19:00,828
[Jinman] Kim Heeju.

269
00:19:00,911 --> 00:19:03,956
Listen, do you realize how serious
this situation is?

270
00:19:04,039 --> 00:19:07,168
Do you have any idea who you're dealing
with right now? Huh?

271
00:19:07,960 --> 00:19:09,879
[Jinman] The situation
is incredibly dangerous.

272
00:19:10,504 --> 00:19:12,506
The Geumseong guys.
Yes Money.

273
00:19:13,048 --> 00:19:14,967
It's only a matter
of time before they track you down.

274
00:19:15,050 --> 00:19:16,343
And once they do, they'll kill you!

275
00:19:16,427 --> 00:19:17,970
-[Jinman] Do you get that?
-Of course I do.

276
00:19:18,596 --> 00:19:22,141
Do you? Really?
Why do this, huh?

277
00:19:22,725 --> 00:19:24,894
[Jinman] Those gold bars
don't belong to you!

278
00:19:24,977 --> 00:19:26,479
They belong to Chairman Ahn!

279
00:19:26,937 --> 00:19:28,981
You can live if you return the gold!

280
00:19:29,565 --> 00:19:31,066
[Jinman] If you're too scared
to give it back,

281
00:19:31,150 --> 00:19:32,276
I'll do it for you.

282
00:19:32,693 --> 00:19:34,153
Then you can leave the country!

283
00:19:34,236 --> 00:19:36,572
I'll help you get a passport
and anything else you need!

284
00:19:36,655 --> 00:19:37,948
[Heeju] Don't lie to me.

285
00:19:38,032 --> 00:19:40,826
What did Chairman Ahn promise you
for handing me over?

286
00:19:40,910 --> 00:19:43,245
Ah, you don't understand
a word I'm saying.

287
00:19:43,329 --> 00:19:44,497
[Heeju] Go!

288
00:19:45,122 --> 00:19:46,707
Just get outta here, please!

289
00:19:46,791 --> 00:19:48,417
If I was going to,

290
00:19:48,501 --> 00:19:50,878
I would have given the gold back
a long time ago!

291
00:19:51,378 --> 00:19:53,005
[Jinman] The gold bars
have completely blinded you

292
00:19:53,088 --> 00:19:54,215
and now you're not thinking straight!

293
00:19:54,298 --> 00:19:56,008
[Jinman] You've completely lost your mind!

294
00:19:56,592 --> 00:19:57,802
Just take a breath, okay?

295
00:19:57,885 --> 00:19:59,678
Let's try and be realistic here.

296
00:20:01,055 --> 00:20:03,265
You can't turn all the bars into cash.

297
00:20:03,349 --> 00:20:04,600
[Jinman] And even if you do,

298
00:20:04,683 --> 00:20:07,061
you realize that's over
100 billion won, right?

299
00:20:07,144 --> 00:20:09,271
How are you gonna spend all
that money before you die?

300
00:20:09,355 --> 00:20:10,523
Huh?

301
00:20:11,023 --> 00:20:12,817
[Jinman] If I return the gold
to Chairman Ahn,

302
00:20:12,900 --> 00:20:14,109
he promised to pay me!

303
00:20:14,652 --> 00:20:16,320
And I'll give all of it to you.

304
00:20:17,571 --> 00:20:19,114
[Jinman] Then you get to live!

305
00:20:19,907 --> 00:20:21,659
You can go somewhere far away!

306
00:20:23,828 --> 00:20:24,912
Like France, huh?

307
00:20:24,995 --> 00:20:26,789
[Jinman] Take your mom
and go to France!

308
00:20:27,498 --> 00:20:29,375
Sound like a plan? Yeah?

309
00:20:29,458 --> 00:20:31,043
[Jinman] Give me the gun.

310
00:20:31,126 --> 00:20:32,002
[gunshot]

311
00:20:34,129 --> 00:20:35,214
Don't you dare move!

312
00:20:38,801 --> 00:20:40,302
Don't follow me.

313
00:20:40,719 --> 00:20:42,304
[Heeju] Don't go looking for me.

314
00:20:42,388 --> 00:20:43,848
And you'd better leave my aunt alone, too!

315
00:20:44,390 --> 00:20:45,599
[car door opens]

316
00:20:46,767 --> 00:20:48,060
[car engine turns over]

317
00:20:48,143 --> 00:20:49,311
Hey, Kim Heeju!

318
00:20:51,188 --> 00:20:52,439
[clangs]

319
00:20:55,109 --> 00:20:56,694
[distant tires squealing]

320
00:20:59,530 --> 00:21:02,533
[car engine revving]
STYLE
::cue()

321
00:21:07,079 --> 00:21:08,372
[exhales]

322
00:21:12,126 --> 00:21:14,670
[cell phone vibrates]

323
00:21:14,753 --> 00:21:17,506
HEEJU

324
00:21:17,590 --> 00:21:19,133
Ah, dammit, seriously?

325
00:21:30,811 --> 00:21:33,814
[cell phone vibrates]

326
00:21:37,902 --> 00:21:39,403
HEEJU

327
00:21:39,904 --> 00:21:41,488
[clears throat]

328
00:21:41,572 --> 00:21:42,740
Hey, Heeju.

329
00:21:43,115 --> 00:21:45,117
[Heeju] Detective Kim tailed me.

330
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:46,994
He just pulled me over.

331
00:21:47,077 --> 00:21:49,622
And he saw the gold bars in my trunk, too.

332
00:21:49,705 --> 00:21:50,706
[Woogy] What?

333
00:21:50,789 --> 00:21:52,249
How did he know to follow you?

334
00:21:52,833 --> 00:21:54,710
[Heeju] I think he was staking out
the hospital.

335
00:21:54,793 --> 00:21:56,629
He had to be listening in.

336
00:21:57,755 --> 00:22:00,341
Somehow he knew everything I said
to my aunt there.

337
00:22:00,424 --> 00:22:01,884
[Woogy] Wait. So then...

338
00:22:03,052 --> 00:22:06,680
...he has to know you're really Kim Heeju
and not Ju Haran.

339
00:22:08,182 --> 00:22:10,184
[Woogy] What about now?
Is he still tailing you?

340
00:22:10,267 --> 00:22:11,936
Uh, no. I'm okay.

341
00:22:12,519 --> 00:22:14,521
I threatened him with the gun and ran.

342
00:22:15,689 --> 00:22:17,107
Okay, good work.

343
00:22:17,191 --> 00:22:19,735
So anyway, now you better just
find somewhere to hide.

344
00:22:19,818 --> 00:22:20,819
And then...

345
00:22:21,695 --> 00:22:23,489
...well, I'll figure out what's going on
and call you.

346
00:22:23,572 --> 00:22:24,573
[Heeju] No.

347
00:22:25,074 --> 00:22:27,952
I don't have time for that.
Where are you now?

348
00:22:28,035 --> 00:22:29,995
[Heeju] Are you still at
the jewelry store?

349
00:22:30,621 --> 00:22:31,956
Did you get the cash yet?

350
00:22:32,039 --> 00:22:34,208
Uh, yeah.

351
00:22:35,125 --> 00:22:36,335
The jewelry store.

352
00:22:36,919 --> 00:22:38,253
I got the cash already.

353
00:22:39,213 --> 00:22:40,798
I'm gonna head that way now.

354
00:22:41,674 --> 00:22:42,883
I'll meet you there.

355
00:22:42,967 --> 00:22:44,218
[cell phone disconnects]

356
00:22:52,184 --> 00:22:53,560
Ah!

357
00:22:56,397 --> 00:22:57,690
[exhales]

358
00:22:57,773 --> 00:22:58,983
Dammit.

359
00:23:00,192 --> 00:23:01,819
[exhales]

360
00:23:01,902 --> 00:23:03,862
[Woogy] Okay, let's just run.

361
00:23:04,822 --> 00:23:06,073
All right.

362
00:23:06,156 --> 00:23:07,992
Fuck it. Whatever.

363
00:23:09,326 --> 00:23:10,869
Yeah, fuck it.
I don't care.

364
00:23:12,746 --> 00:23:14,081
Ah, fuck.

365
00:23:14,164 --> 00:23:17,167
[tires squealing]
[car horns honking]

366
00:23:24,049 --> 00:23:25,134
[cell phone trilling]

367
00:23:25,217 --> 00:23:27,136
Hey, I'm almost there now.
What about you?

368
00:23:28,846 --> 00:23:30,097
[Heeju] Are you there yet?

369
00:23:30,180 --> 00:23:31,473
Yeah, I'm here already.

370
00:23:31,557 --> 00:23:33,475
[Heeju] You are?
I don't see you.

371
00:23:34,351 --> 00:23:36,061
[Woogy] Do you see me waving
at the end of the alley?

372
00:23:38,856 --> 00:23:42,026
Oh. Yeah, I see you.
STYLE
::cue()

373
00:23:42,693 --> 00:23:43,694
Is that your car?

374
00:23:44,403 --> 00:23:46,030
Here, over here.
You can park--

375
00:23:50,659 --> 00:23:52,036
Uh, hey, Heeju.

376
00:23:52,119 --> 00:23:53,954
I think the guys are here.
Open the window. The window.

377
00:23:54,038 --> 00:23:55,330
Hurry. Open it. The window.

378
00:23:56,749 --> 00:23:58,459
Hey, isn't that Woogy?

379
00:23:59,918 --> 00:24:01,336
The window. Just open it.

380
00:24:01,795 --> 00:24:02,796
The window?

381
00:24:07,301 --> 00:24:08,427
-[Moonsu] Get him!
-[Woogy] Heeju!

382
00:24:08,510 --> 00:24:11,138
In my car! I got the gold bars
and the cash.

383
00:24:11,221 --> 00:24:12,556
[Woogy] Go get 'em!

384
00:24:12,639 --> 00:24:13,974
And then go hide somewhere! Hurry!

385
00:24:14,058 --> 00:24:15,184
-[Heeju] Hello?
-[Moonsu] Hey!

386
00:24:15,267 --> 00:24:16,935
[Woogy] Shit!
[breathing heavily]

387
00:24:17,019 --> 00:24:18,145
[Moonsu] Woogy!

388
00:24:19,146 --> 00:24:21,106
Woogy? You there?

389
00:24:26,070 --> 00:24:27,071
[Moonsu] Ah!

390
00:24:27,154 --> 00:24:29,490
[crowd shouting]

391
00:24:29,573 --> 00:24:32,076
[Moonsu] Son of a bitch!
Woogy!

392
00:24:33,702 --> 00:24:36,705
[Woogy breathing heavily]

393
00:24:37,706 --> 00:24:40,292
[Moonsu] Hey! Stop!

394
00:24:42,377 --> 00:24:44,213
-[Moonsu] Guys, split up!
-This way.

395
00:24:44,296 --> 00:24:45,339
[Henchman B] Come on!

396
00:24:46,131 --> 00:24:48,342
[Moonsu] Hey! You motherfucker!

397
00:24:48,425 --> 00:24:51,053
[Woogy breathing erratically]

398
00:24:52,888 --> 00:24:54,264
[all groaning]

399
00:24:54,932 --> 00:24:57,559
[Moonsu] What the fuck?
Go, go, go, go, go, go!

400
00:25:01,146 --> 00:25:02,147
[Moonsu] Get him!

401
00:25:02,231 --> 00:25:03,899
[Woogy breathing heavily]

402
00:25:06,985 --> 00:25:09,196
[Woogy groaning]

403
00:25:09,279 --> 00:25:10,280
Come on, man.
We're like brothers.

404
00:25:10,364 --> 00:25:12,491
-Let's go, Woogy.
-[Woogy] Can't we talk it out?

405
00:25:12,574 --> 00:25:14,827
Stay back!
I said stay back, for fuck's sake!

406
00:25:16,495 --> 00:25:17,746
[Woogy] Don't come any closer.

407
00:25:17,830 --> 00:25:19,665
Ah, fuck this shit!

408
00:25:19,748 --> 00:25:20,833
[grunts]

409
00:25:20,916 --> 00:25:22,334
Shit, shit!

410
00:25:22,417 --> 00:25:23,710
[shouts]

411
00:25:24,837 --> 00:25:26,547
Shit, shit.

412
00:25:26,630 --> 00:25:28,257
-[groaning]
-[Moonsu] Ah, fuck!

413
00:25:28,340 --> 00:25:29,675
He went that way!
Come on, let's go!

414
00:25:30,968 --> 00:25:32,886
[breathing heavily]

415
00:25:32,970 --> 00:25:34,263
Oh, shit.

416
00:25:41,645 --> 00:25:44,106
Ah, fuck's sake.

417
00:25:44,189 --> 00:25:46,400
[labored breathing]

418
00:25:46,483 --> 00:25:47,860
Ah, shit.

419
00:25:50,654 --> 00:25:52,156
[door creaks]

420
00:25:52,698 --> 00:25:53,740
[grunts]

421
00:25:53,824 --> 00:25:55,450
[door locking]

422
00:25:55,826 --> 00:25:58,036
[groaning]

423
00:26:05,252 --> 00:26:06,879
[banging on door]

424
00:26:06,962 --> 00:26:08,380
[Moonsu] Woogy, open up!

425
00:26:09,882 --> 00:26:11,049
[Moonsu] I'm gonna break it down!

426
00:26:11,675 --> 00:26:12,759
You hear me?

427
00:26:12,843 --> 00:26:13,969
[groans]

428
00:26:14,052 --> 00:26:15,262
[banging on door]

429
00:26:15,345 --> 00:26:17,222
[Moonsu] Woogy!
STYLE
::cue()

430
00:26:24,521 --> 00:26:27,733
[cell phone vibrates]

431
00:26:27,816 --> 00:26:28,942
Woogy, hey.

432
00:26:29,318 --> 00:26:31,236
[Woogy breathing heavily]
[Woogy] Heeju.

433
00:26:31,904 --> 00:26:33,405
[panting]

434
00:26:33,488 --> 00:26:35,532
What are you gonna do with that money?

435
00:26:35,616 --> 00:26:37,534
What are you talking about?

436
00:26:37,618 --> 00:26:39,119
Tell me where you are, please.

437
00:26:40,204 --> 00:26:42,206
I've seen it happen over and over.

438
00:26:42,873 --> 00:26:43,999
[Moonsu] Hey, Woogy!

439
00:26:44,583 --> 00:26:47,461
Stupid people who got greedy
and ruined their lives.

440
00:26:47,961 --> 00:26:49,713
My father was one of those guys.

441
00:26:49,796 --> 00:26:52,799
[Moonsu] Open the door while
I'm asking nicely. 'Kay?

442
00:26:53,342 --> 00:26:55,594
And fuck me.
I guess I got greedy, too.

443
00:26:57,638 --> 00:26:59,723
[Woogy] I didn't even get
to spend all the money.

444
00:27:00,682 --> 00:27:02,351
Just tell me where you are right now.

445
00:27:03,018 --> 00:27:04,561
Did you get away from those guys?

446
00:27:05,646 --> 00:27:07,231
[Moonsu] Hey, motherfucker!

447
00:27:07,314 --> 00:27:08,899
Just open the door!

448
00:27:08,982 --> 00:27:10,317
-Heeju.
-[Moonsu] Huh?

449
00:27:11,818 --> 00:27:12,945
Open up!

450
00:27:14,696 --> 00:27:16,365
I won't last long at the farm, okay?

451
00:27:16,448 --> 00:27:18,533
-[Moonsu] You son of a bitch!
-I'll give up your name.

452
00:27:19,993 --> 00:27:24,289
[Woogy] So as soon as we hang up,
you need to run as far as you can.

453
00:27:25,165 --> 00:27:26,458
You can take all the gold.

454
00:27:26,750 --> 00:27:28,377
-[Moonsu] Break the door down.
-You'll find it in the trunk

455
00:27:28,460 --> 00:27:29,920
with the cash.
All of it is there.

456
00:27:30,003 --> 00:27:31,088
[Moonsu] Harder, you idiot!

457
00:27:31,171 --> 00:27:33,256
Take everything.
Take it and run.

458
00:27:33,340 --> 00:27:35,258
-[Woogy] Got it?
-Hey, you just--

459
00:27:35,342 --> 00:27:38,178
just make it as long as you can.
I'll--I'll be there right away.

460
00:27:38,762 --> 00:27:40,389
[Woogy] You know
what this reminds me of?

461
00:27:41,807 --> 00:27:43,350
When we used to play freeze tag.

462
00:27:44,184 --> 00:27:46,019
[bangs on door]
[Moonsu groans]

463
00:27:46,103 --> 00:27:48,188
I got tagged in the mining town
and had to freeze.

464
00:27:48,271 --> 00:27:49,398
[Moonsu] What are you doing?

465
00:27:49,898 --> 00:27:51,274
[Moonsu] Try lifting it.

466
00:27:51,733 --> 00:27:53,777
I was so scared until you tagged me.

467
00:27:53,860 --> 00:27:54,903
[Moonsu] Break the whole thing down!

468
00:27:54,987 --> 00:27:56,321
[door bangs]

469
00:27:56,405 --> 00:27:57,781
You really forgot all that?

470
00:27:57,864 --> 00:27:58,991
[door clanging]

471
00:27:59,616 --> 00:28:00,742
[exhales]

472
00:28:00,826 --> 00:28:01,994
-Woogy--
-[Woogy] I gotta go.

473
00:28:02,077 --> 00:28:03,870
-[Moonsu] Open it, fucker!
-Wait a minute.

474
00:28:03,954 --> 00:28:05,288
-Woogy? Hey!
-[Moonsu] The fuck are you doing?

475
00:28:05,831 --> 00:28:07,290
[breathing heavily]
[phone disconnects]

476
00:28:07,374 --> 00:28:10,377
[grunting]
[clanging]

477
00:28:11,461 --> 00:28:14,464
[all breathing heavily]

478
00:28:20,387 --> 00:28:21,388
[Moonsu] Woogy.

479
00:28:22,055 --> 00:28:23,098
Let's go.

480
00:28:26,059 --> 00:28:27,978
[exhales]

481
00:28:28,061 --> 00:28:29,604
Oh, what do I do?

482
00:28:31,565 --> 00:28:34,067
[car engine turns over]

483
00:28:36,820 --> 00:28:38,363
[exhales]

484
00:28:45,328 --> 00:28:46,329
The gold bars are in the trunk.

485
00:28:47,664 --> 00:28:48,707
[Dokyung] Heeju.

486
00:28:50,417 --> 00:28:53,128
I'll sell the gold bars
and I'll come right back.
STYLE
::cue()

487
00:28:53,879 --> 00:28:54,880
[grunts]

488
00:28:55,464 --> 00:28:56,506
Don't bother.

489
00:28:57,215 --> 00:28:59,384
This will be the last time
we see each other.

490
00:29:00,218 --> 00:29:01,970
[Dokyung] You still have
Ju Haran's account, right?

491
00:29:02,721 --> 00:29:04,347
Once I get the cash for the gold,

492
00:29:04,431 --> 00:29:06,349
I'll wire the money back
to the bank account.

493
00:29:07,601 --> 00:29:09,144
What? Why?

494
00:29:09,227 --> 00:29:10,854
[Dokyung] Because you don't trust me
right now.

495
00:29:12,606 --> 00:29:13,607
So...

496
00:29:14,524 --> 00:29:16,860
I wanna make sure you get your half first.

497
00:29:18,653 --> 00:29:21,114
You wanna break up because you're afraid
I'll take everything.

498
00:29:22,199 --> 00:29:23,200
But...

499
00:29:24,910 --> 00:29:27,496
...now that I have my share,
I know what matters.

500
00:29:28,538 --> 00:29:29,915
I can lose everything else.

501
00:29:30,749 --> 00:29:32,042
But I can't lose you, Heeju.

502
00:29:32,709 --> 00:29:34,211
[exhales]

503
00:29:34,294 --> 00:29:35,420
Come on.

504
00:29:37,297 --> 00:29:39,549
Ah, what's happening here, huh?

505
00:29:41,009 --> 00:29:42,844
[Donggu] Is this the guy getting on
the ferry?

506
00:29:43,887 --> 00:29:44,888
Yeah.

507
00:29:45,889 --> 00:29:46,890
Oh.

508
00:29:47,808 --> 00:29:49,810
Pay up. Money.

509
00:29:49,893 --> 00:29:51,019
-[Donggu] Come on. Money, money.
-Uh...

510
00:29:54,940 --> 00:29:55,941
You can check it.

511
00:29:58,360 --> 00:29:59,361
[zipper unzips]

512
00:30:03,073 --> 00:30:04,074
[exhales]

513
00:30:04,658 --> 00:30:05,867
Let's go.

514
00:30:05,951 --> 00:30:07,202
[car door closes]

515
00:30:07,285 --> 00:30:09,162
[car engine turns over]

516
00:30:11,206 --> 00:30:12,374
[car door closes]

517
00:30:16,920 --> 00:30:18,046
[gears shifting]

518
00:30:20,757 --> 00:30:23,593
[engine rumbling]

519
00:30:25,887 --> 00:30:28,515
[engine revving]

520
00:30:39,359 --> 00:30:40,777
[car alarm beeps]

521
00:30:43,363 --> 00:30:45,866
[grunting]

522
00:30:47,868 --> 00:30:49,828
[breathing heavily]

523
00:30:51,538 --> 00:30:52,539
